==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stepchild
<hw>Step"child`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>ste⟦oacute⟧pcild</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A bereaved child;
one who has lost father or mother.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A son or daughter of one's wife or husband by a
former marriage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stepdame</ent>⟦br⟧
